DFT calculations were further conducted to reveal qualitatively the modified electron transfer between SnS2 and the matrix upon forming covalent bridging. The model systems were optimized based on the (2 × 2) SnS2 monolayer on (6 × 6) graphene matrix (GRAPHENE or G). As known, the charge density changes (Δρ) can be acquired by Eq. (1):1Δρ=ρA-SnS2@G-ρSnS2-ρgraphene\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
